Since `map_val 0 = 0` (as `0` in the image of `valuation K` maps to `0` in `valuation L`), we have `valuation L (algebraMap K L r.1) ≤ 0`.
This proves that `algebraMap K L r.1` is in `↑(valuation L).integer`.

